            "title": "英超｜曼城僅剩2條戰線 哥迪奧拿目標明確：爭入英超前4",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曼城領隊哥迪奧拿。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e9acc3bdef4ca1bc0946ed128c542a65/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250222/_2025022211123297274.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曼城領隊哥迪奧拿。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英超4連霸的曼城今季表現大跌，隨著周中歐聯出局後今季只剩下2條戰線。衛冕英超基本無望下，領隊哥迪奧拿直言餘下球季的目標非常明確，是全力爭取打入聯賽前4，以取得下季歐聯資格。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e3b7d1e26208e73ef8daf5ffe6377b4/2025-02/2025-02-11T214826Z_599765531_UP1EL2B1OKPVY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-MCI-RMA-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06cb9ac6414727684e410d3e9503d570/2025-02/2025-02-15T152835Z_384222342_UP1EL2F16ZMIZ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MCI-NEW-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b64f4ae7027f70ba4a0c3e26a845c113/2025-02/2025-02-15T160734Z_2110834351_UP1EL2F18SKOL_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MCI-NEW-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0174dc086daba9463fc95fb259584763/2025-02/2025-02-15T162547Z_666956656_UP1EL2F19MXR0_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MCI-NEW-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城領隊哥迪奧拿。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a95f4daffd60c9f326ecdc3003019292/2025-02/2025-02-19T202954Z_981556215_UP1EL2J1KXS1N_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-MCI-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城領隊哥迪奧拿。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/42e785828ebefae48104b79e8849abe8/2025-02/2025-02-19T212413Z_1298616760_UP1EL2J1NGB5Q_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-MCI-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/20e815a99bff7825803d45105c08c21b/2025-02/2025-02-19T213611Z_1440921329_UP1EL2J1O0A6W_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-MCI-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4cbb11e81398bd628833c23d3a95daf9/2025-02/2025-02-19T213649Z_1618635221_UP1EL2J1O1B71_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CHAMPIONS-RMA-MCI-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼城今季表現不穩。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>曼城只剩2條戰線</h2>\n<p>曼城今季表現大倒退，於周中歐聯附加賽不敵皇家馬德里後，錄首次在哥迪奧拿麾下不入16強，連同聯賽盃出局，藍月今季只剩下英超和足總盃2條戰線。不過，曼城目前在英超只得13勝5和7負排第4位，落後榜首利物浦17分，基本上衛冕無望。\n\n</p><h2>哥帥目標爭前4</h2>\n<p>雖然曼城目前排第4位，但其實他們只領先第9位的阿士東維拉5分，故前4之爭非常激烈。藍月領隊哥迪奧拿也直言保住前4是今季的最大目標：「英超對我們而言十分重要。其實我們近來在聯賽的表現不錯，但問題是不夠穩定。我們必須努力爭取保住前4位置，希望取得下季歐聯入場劵。」<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
